---
title: "Archive"
description: "Historical versions of posts kept for reference. These posts may be outdated or superseded."
permalink: /archive/
---
{% extends "layouts/page.njk" %}

{% block pageContent %}
<div class="page-meta">
  {{ collections.archivedPosts | length }} archived post{% if (collections.archivedPosts | length) != 1 %}s{% endif %}
</div>
<p>
  Archived posts are historical versions of posts kept for reference. Each archived post has a link to the current version.
</p>



{% if (collections.archivedPosts | length) > 0 %}
<ul class="post-list">
  {% for post in collections.archivedPosts %}
    <li>
      {% linkedPost post.url %}
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
{% else %}
<p>No archived posts yet.</p>
{% endif %}

{% endblock %}